# File Naming Conventions

## Route Files

All route files MUST use kebab-case naming:

**✓ CORRECT:**
```
src/routes/clinic-routes.ts
src/routes/client-routes.ts
src/routes/appointment-routes.ts
src/routes/payment-routes.ts
src/routes/contact-history-routes.ts
src/routes/insurance-company-address-routes.ts
```

**❌ WRONG:**
```
src/routes/clinicRoutes.ts        (camelCase)
src/routes/ClientRoutes.ts        (PascalCase)
src/routes/clinic_routes.ts       (snake_case)
```

## Import Statement Pattern

When importing routes in [src/routes/index.ts](mdc:src/routes/index.ts), always use kebab-case filenames:

```typescript
// ✓ CORRECT
import clinicRoutes from './clinic-routes';
import clientRoutes from './client-routes';
import advancedBillingRoutes from './advanced-billing-routes';

// ❌ WRONG
import clinicRoutes from './clinicRoutes';
import clientRoutes from './clientRoutes';
import advancedBillingRoutes from './advancedBillingRoutes';
```

## Model Files

Model files use PascalCase with .ts extension:

**✓ CORRECT:**
```
src/models/Client.ts
src/models/Payment.ts
src/models/Order.ts
src/models/Appointment.ts
```

## Service Files

Service files use PascalCase ending with Service:

**✓ CORRECT:**
```
src/services/ClientService.ts
src/services/PaymentService.ts
src/services/OrderService.ts
src/services/ClinicService.ts
```

## Controller Files

Controller files use PascalCase ending with Controller:

**✓ CORRECT:**
```
src/controllers/ClientController.ts
src/controllers/PaymentController.ts
src/controllers/OrderController.ts
```

## Directory Structure

Directory names use kebab-case:

**✓ CORRECT:**
```
src/models/
src/services/
src/controllers/
src/routes/
src/utils/
src/middleware/
src/views/
```

## Summary

| Component | Convention | Example |
|-----------|-----------|---------|
| Routes | kebab-case | `client-routes.ts` |
| Models | PascalCase | `Client.ts` |
| Services | PascalCase | `ClientService.ts` |
| Controllers | PascalCase | `ClientController.ts` |
| Utils/Helpers | camelCase | `mongooseHelpers.ts` |
| Directories | kebab-case | `src/routes/` |